flowchart TB

Candidate[Khu vuc ung vien]

Candidate --> ProfileMe[Ho so cua toi /Profile/Me]
Candidate --> UserCVs[Quan ly CV /UserCVs]
Candidate --> CandidateApps[Don ung tuyen cua toi /CandidateApplications]
Candidate --> CandidateInvitations[Loi moi nhan duoc /CandidateInvitations]
Candidate --> SavedItems[Muc da luu /Stars/Saved]
Candidate --> Notifications[Thong bao /Notifications]
Candidate --> AccountSettings[Cai dat tai khoan /AccountSettings]

ProfileMe --> ProfileView[Xem ho so /Profile/ViewProfile/:id]
ProfileMe --> ProfileEdit[Cap nhat ho so /Profile/Edit/:id]

ProfileEdit --> AddEducation[Them hoc van /Profile/AddEducation]
ProfileEdit --> UpdateEducation[Cap nhat hoc van /Profile/UpdateEducation]
ProfileEdit --> DeleteEducation[Xoa hoc van /Profile/DeleteEducation]
ProfileEdit --> AddExperience[Them kinh nghiem /Profile/AddExperience]
ProfileEdit --> UpdateExperience[Cap nhat kinh nghiem /Profile/UpdateExperience]
ProfileEdit --> DeleteExperience[Xoa kinh nghiem /Profile/DeleteExperience]
ProfileEdit --> AddProject[Them du an /Profile/AddProject]
ProfileEdit --> UpdateProject[Cap nhat du an /Profile/UpdateProject]
ProfileEdit --> DeleteProject[Xoa du an /Profile/DeleteProject]
ProfileEdit --> AddSkill[Them ky nang /Profile/AddSkill]
ProfileEdit --> UpdateSkill[Cap nhat ky nang /Profile/UpdateSkill]
ProfileEdit --> DeleteSkill[Xoa ky nang /Profile/DeleteSkill]

UserCVs --> UploadCV[Tai CV /UserCVs/Upload]
UserCVs --> SetDefaultCV[Dat CV mac dinh /UserCVs/SetDefault/:id]

CandidateApps --> InterviewDetails[Chi tiet phong van /CandidateApplications/InterviewDetails/:id]

CandidateInvitations --> InvitationDetails[Chi tiet loi moi /CandidateInvitations/Details/:id]
CandidateInvitations --> AcceptInvitation[Chap nhan loi moi /CandidateInvitations/Accept/:id]
CandidateInvitations --> DeclineInvitation[Tu choi loi moi /CandidateInvitations/Decline/:id]

SavedItems --> StarredBy[Danh sach nguoi da luu /Stars/StarredBy]
Notifications --> OpenNotification[Mo thong bao /Notifications/Open/:id]
Notifications --> MarkAllRead[Danh dau da doc /Notifications/MarkAllAsRead]
